		"description": "{html}<div><p>It would be nice to be able to use the searchBar attached to the\ntableView to get remote results.</p>\n<p>Like an option to skip searching the local tableView. Then you\ncan bind the \"event\" yourself and fill the tableView with the\nresults.</p></div>{html}",
		"attachment": [],
